Name: Qublyne Dungeons
About the game: An engaging retro vibe arcade to relax and overpass your achievements with every game. Pickup resources and use them to aquire physical and magical powers of your choice to defeat opponents while avoiding obstacles and traps in your path. Complement your play sessions with a suitable generated game environment, lighting mood and ambient track of you liking to get the game rhythm going. ITEMS Use over 30 physical and magical items at your will to defeat your opponents. ENEMY`s Combat with over 15 types of enemy`s with different skills and abilities. TRAPS and OBSTACLES Use your skills to avoid the many traps and obstacles in your path. RESOURCES Collect and use resources at your disposal to achieve your goals. MUSIC and MOOD Choose a suiting sountrack and ambient mood to complement your play style. CHALLENGES Take on challenges and boast your highest scores.
